data.description: Updated acreage walkout-ranch in a private neighborhood!  This home has it all: tons of updates, tons of square footage, and with a 1.34 acre yard, tons of room to enjoy your property. Tall ceilings, formal dining room, eat in kitchen, and a huge primary suite are just some of the highlights on the main level.  The finished walkout basement has tons of room for entertaining or recreation.  Outside you will find an oversized deck, lower level patio from the walk-out basement, a cozy patio outside the front door, a fenced in area, and plenty of room for an outbuilding. Schedule your showing today to find out how you can make this dream house your home!
